                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-134435064" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="134435064">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/flyya2004/">浊越星</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2009-06-29</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">一是很适合GRE作文的论证，二是此人真能讲，三是此人的遭遇真悲惨</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
